name: Paperless Tiger_01
description:
Paperless Tiger_01

Paperless Tiger_01 is an artwork adapted from Celyn Bricker’s  AI generated series Art For All to make a special edition for Chinese New Year, creating a new pattern that references a ‘chuang hua’ or traditional window decoration. However hidden in the pattern of this artwork are a number of tiger footprints, which relates to the estimated number of wild tigers still remaining in China. 

无纸老虎—01

无纸老虎—01 是改编自 Celyn Bricker 的 人工智能 Art For All 系列的艺术作品，为虎年春节制别版窗花作品。 同时，这件艺术品的图案中隐藏着许多老虎的脚印，脚印的数量也代表着中国境内野生老虎的估计数量。
